First programs

Task 1 
Create a new project and a new .py file within it. In the created file, write a program that will display "Hello world!"

Task 2
Write a program that asks for a name and then displays a welcome message with the name provided (e.g., "Hello, Hubert!")

Task 3 
Write a program that asks the user for the current year and year of birth, then calculates the user's current age and displays a message (e.g., "You are 25 years old")

Task 4
Write a program that calculates how many hours and minutes it is based on the number of minutes entered

